name: Instagram UI Kit
description:
Updated UI kit and template of Instagram's stories, posts and post grid! The kit includes:


Instagram stories view and widgets:

  • Countdown
  • Ask a question
  • Polls
  • Quiz
  • Emoji Slider
  • Hastags
  • Mentions and locations


Instagram Feed:

  • Sponsored posts
  • User profile
  • Following/non-following profiles
  • User profile's grid
